caption: Deadly Weapon
created: 20260405120000000
modified: 20260405120000000
title: Policy1435(I)(A)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

means "any weapon, whether loaded or unloaded, from which a shot may be discharged, or a switchblade knife, gravity knife, billy, blackjack, bludgeon, or metal knuckles." Conn. Gen. Stat. § 53a-3 (6).
